-- Ordonez: Restructuring Greek debt would be error
-- 
-- Fri Jun 3, 2011 5:05am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/06/03/us-spain-ordonez-greece-idUSTRE7521Q720110603

 

 SITGES, Spain  (Reuters) - Restructuring of Greek debt would be a mistake, Bank of Spain Governor Miguel Angel Fernandez Ordonez said on Friday. 

 "On the issue of restructuring the debt, I say no," Ordonez said at a conference in northern Spain. (Reporting by Nigel Davies and Paul Day)